<br>
If you're on Giant positive faction, well, the faction adjustments are a bonus for you.<br>
<br>
If you are (or plan to be) on Claws of Veeshan faction, and you're &lt; 55,  you probably wont be &quot;allowed&quot; into the Halls of Testing for CoV faction armor yet.  <br>
Find a group that's on Giant faction and see if you can tag along with them for the spell (other drops, like the talismans, are nice as well).  You have time (after getting the spell) to go to Kael Drakkel and get your CoV faction back.<br>
